---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 413
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Heterodoxy And Deviation
By: Eckhart
---
Eight heavens are often spoken of and nine choirs of angels; there is
nothing of that where I am. You must know that expressions of that
sort, which conjure up pictures in the mind, merely serve as
allurements to God. In God there is nothing but God.
